{"tid":2212300,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好討厭用social media ？","createTime":"2020-09-21T16:37:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T15:58:20.000Z","uid":262886,"like":292,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"ef94db9b9f6261f54dfdf7739af1d71070bdcbb4","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:37:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人好討厭用social media ？<br />\n唔知幾時開始，越嚟越發覺社交媒體束縛緊我嘅思想<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每朝起身要掃吓facebook，冇嘢做又要掃吓IG<br />\n根本漫無目的，浪費好多無謂時間<br />\n就好似慢性吸毒上咗癮，成為日常生活一個routine 習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次睇social media 就好似窺探緊人地生活私隱<br />\n例如每日三餐post stories 食過咩<br />\n去過咩聚會，見過咩朋友<br />\n甚至有啲癲到同邊個傾咗幾耐電話<br />\ncap埋whatsapp對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明白用得Social media 係想開心share <br />\n但發覺好多人個心態係想包裝自己<br />\n話比全世界聽自己過得好風光<br />\n或者一係就放負想人關心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但諗深究竟friend list 𥚃面又幾多個我真係熟，我又好想了解嘅？根本好多只係有一面之緣，或者係舊同學<br />\n本來各有各生活亦無再聯繫，但一打開social media，發覺同人距離拉得太近，好唔自在舒服，人地嘅生活好似慘入咗自己嘅生活，<br />\n明明好多嘢根本我就唔撚想知，但資訊變得好泛濫，越睇越疲累，甚至會影響情緒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家冇再用正身fb ig <br />\n開咗個空白fb ac打任務同用twitter睇新聞，即刻覺得成個世界清靜咗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3aeb2417b6bf80dff5a64d11b06f5fb2d7f619","tid":2212300,"uid":71508,"like":37,"dislike":58,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"唔用嘅一定係毒撚<br />\n因為同人比較之下<br />\n自己嘅生活幾咁無聊<br />\n但人地咁多姿多采<br />\n之後就會懶清高"},{"pid":"345d00f0f1018649066284e2d1cd15c09d885e80","tid":2212300,"uid":79793,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"依家開IG就為左睇貓睇膠睇文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班朋友變哂P圖怪獸呃毒撚，明明出到黎個樣都唔係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85e8b2673e59777be70b63cb202b6ea281a5a56","tid":2212300,"uid":163024,"like":37,"dislike":4,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kj5zjPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkj5zjPH.png&h=0182f38e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tYhhBv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tYhhBv.png&h=7719efe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6252c6d32ad49a032dfe961d126fb706ec16f66","tid":2212300,"uid":14348,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"你岩呀 social media 就係俾人去表現一個理想中嘅自己。"},{"pid":"e76ce1aa38e1b33e5c0c53c2ded9f5181c9193ee","tid":2212300,"uid":192075,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"我當fb ig雜誌咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7818d30c939debb8ce640d2529c7b5cedd5cbf","tid":2212300,"uid":139173,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"可以打咁多字即係你唔討厭網上溝通<br />\n只不過係因為嗰啲平台令你冇存在感<br />\n所以你唔鍾意咁解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226392958902a4921e2e034d8b524f9fa9f48999","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"df3aeb2417b6bf80dff5a64d11b06f5fb2d7f619","tid":2212300,"uid":71508,"like":37,"dislike":58,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:39:26.000Z","msg":"唔用嘅一定係毒撚<br />\n因為同人比較之下<br />\n自己嘅生活幾咁無聊<br />\n但人地咁多姿多采<br />\n之後就會懶清高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"其實有排好沉迷用，乜都post 一餐<br />\n朋友食飯要自拍打卡，食前又要影<br />\n邊去旅行要邊update <br />\n但係去到一個位，我開始問自己post嚟為咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留念？記錄？想分享比邊個<br />\n通過社交媒體，我窺視緊人地生活，同時原來人地窺視自己，的確無形係會産生比較"},{"pid":"199e6d5eba6190499416cf9656207eb24ab3c258","tid":2212300,"uid":62841,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"上得癮嘅都心智唔成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594561ad720dea10ef9420cfea29efb0e7e91f51","tid":2212300,"uid":348821,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"大部分人都靠social media認識你<br />\nSocial media就好似你個CV咁<br />\n包裝到最靚嗰一面比人睇<br />\n都係為咗討好人地<br />\n慢慢好似所有生活都係基於為咗「呃like」咁"},{"pid":"e16133bee9a4e97747a1c32e3650a96f2cf64d94","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"4d7818d30c939debb8ce640d2529c7b5cedd5cbf","tid":2212300,"uid":139173,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:47:06.000Z","msg":"可以打咁多字即係你唔討厭網上溝通<br />\n只不過係因為嗰啲平台令你冇存在感<br />\n所以你唔鍾意咁解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:05:59.000Z","msg":"唔討厭，同熟嘅朋友text分享係好開心<br />\n或者實際見面互相分享<br />\n但係社交平台friend list 好多根本朋友都稱唔上，感覺唔知為咩post <br />\n當然連登匿名分享，感覺舒服好多，冇比人窺視嘅感覺"},{"pid":"2430fecb8ca377934a610890d5c21d97ff6cb367","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"594561ad720dea10ef9420cfea29efb0e7e91f51","tid":2212300,"uid":348821,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"大部分人都靠social media認識你<br />\nSocial media就好似你個CV咁<br />\n包裝到最靚嗰一面比人睇<br />\n都係為咗討好人地<br />\n慢慢好似所有生活都係基於為咗「呃like」咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"比起透過social media 認識我<br />\n我更希望係現實認識我係咩人<br />\n熟嘅有交情嘅本身已經知我係咩人<br />\n咁我用social media 究竟係包裝比邊個睇？"},{"pid":"ffd02b85a60516831b9b468fc7ff43230225e857","tid":2212300,"uid":348821,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2430fecb8ca377934a610890d5c21d97ff6cb367","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"594561ad720dea10ef9420cfea29efb0e7e91f51","tid":2212300,"uid":348821,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"大部分人都靠social media認識你<br />\nSocial media就好似你個CV咁<br />\n包裝到最靚嗰一面比人睇<br />\n都係為咗討好人地<br />\n慢慢好似所有生活都係基於為咗「呃like」咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"比起透過social media 認識我<br />\n我更希望係現實認識我係咩人<br />\n熟嘅有交情嘅本身已經知我係咩人<br />\n咁我用social media 究竟係包裝比邊個睇？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"冇錯最理想緊係現實認識最好啦<br />\n不過現實邊有咁理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSocial media就係比啲唔熟嘅人睇<br />\n透過social media了解你生活、興趣、喜好、甚至朋友圈子<br />\n經過篩選再進一步了解，可能係dm 傾下計再約出黎現實認識<br />\n所以某程度上都係幫你實現緊現實認識你嘅方法"},{"pid":"56cdea56165ee44d293dab13c748bbc66b1187e7","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ffd02b85a60516831b9b468fc7ff43230225e857","tid":2212300,"uid":348821,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2430fecb8ca377934a610890d5c21d97ff6cb367","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"594561ad720dea10ef9420cfea29efb0e7e91f51","tid":2212300,"uid":348821,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"大部分人都靠social media認識你<br />\nSocial media就好似你個CV咁<br />\n包裝到最靚嗰一面比人睇<br />\n都係為咗討好人地<br />\n慢慢好似所有生活都係基於為咗「呃like」咁"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"比起透過social media 認識我<br />\n我更希望係現實認識我係咩人<br />\n熟嘅有交情嘅本身已經知我係咩人<br />\n咁我用social media 究竟係包裝比邊個睇？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:18:00.000Z","msg":"冇錯最理想緊係現實認識最好啦<br />\n不過現實邊有咁理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSocial media就係比啲唔熟嘅人睇<br />\n透過social media了解你生活、興趣、喜好、甚至朋友圈子<br />\n經過篩選再進一步了解，可能係dm 傾下計再約出黎現實認識<br />\n所以某程度上都係幫你實現緊現實認識你嘅方法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"都係，你有你道理<br />\n但我覺得距離突然拉得太近，好冇私隱<br />\n可能我傳統，識親嘅都係現實啱傾，慢慢就好自然成為朋友<br />\n自己幾位best friends，分別都有開ac，但從來唔用唔post 嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5262e1ab31340b5e3a231c9aaae914cc1fba132d","tid":2212300,"uid":3852,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:37:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人social media只係用嚟睇新聞睇貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有add人都係之前add落，同其他人冇乜互動"},{"pid":"37255fb8595b1eb8d0a8cbaffb9103435be4ebb8","tid":2212300,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:38:37.000Z","msg":"矯情"},{"pid":"bbc79733312136fb8b197da82e17074d1282209e","tid":2212300,"uid":15230,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"建議樓主睇下Netflix套social dilemma<br />\nexactly講緊呢樣嘢，而呢啲social media platform係designed to be addicted<br />\n利申：做緊呢行，無得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35599fd64f850f3850befd221c05b33c7c44c220","tid":2212300,"uid":249026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"+1<br />\n但又好懷念以前msn既日子<br />\n一對一<br />\n用keyboard打字又夠快"},{"pid":"36593f5230bb888eb70b4e691a43e3299101a630","tid":2212300,"uid":262886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bbc79733312136fb8b197da82e17074d1282209e","tid":2212300,"uid":15230,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:39:57.000Z","msg":"建議樓主睇下Netflix套social dilemma<br />\nexactly講緊呢樣嘢，而呢啲social media platform係designed to be addicted<br />\n利申：做緊呢行，無得避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T17:56:41.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打介紹，有時間會睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif